136
00:31:44,160 --> 00:31:45,519
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo razgovarati sljedećih pet dana.

137
00:31:45,920 --> 00:31:46,640
[SPEAKER_00] Siguran sam da bismo mogli.

138
00:31:47,359 --> 00:31:49,680
[SPEAKER_00] I siguran sam da ćemo to učiniti s vremenom.

139
00:31:49,839 --> 00:31:52,559
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, dok razmišljam o više stvari, dodati ću ih.

140
00:31:52,559 --> 00:31:53,599
[SPEAKER_01] u odjeljak za komentare.

141
00:31:53,920 --> 00:31:54,160
[SPEAKER_01] Savršeno.

